query: SELECT s.attribute_id, s.attribute_id, s.attribute_name FROM Attribute_Definitions AS s WHERE  s.attribute_id >= 3 ORDER BY s.attribute_id DESC LIMIT 10

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT catalog_level_name), catalog_id FROM Catalog_Contents_Additional_Attributes JOIN Catalog_Structure ON Catalog_Structure.catalog_level_number = Catalog_Contents_Additional_Attributes.catalog_level_number ORDER BY catalog_id DESC

SELECT AVG(u.catalog_id), MIN(u.catalog_id), COUNT(DISTINCT u.catalog_name) FROM Catalogs AS u WHERE  u.catalog_id != 55 AND date_of_publication = (SELECT SUM(date_of_publication) FROM Catalogs AS c WHERE c.catalog_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  c.catalog_id > 75 LIMIT 2) LIMIT 7
SELECT attribute_id, attribute_name FROM Attribute_Definitions WHERE  attribute_id < 78 GROUP BY attribute_name HAVING MAX(attribute_id) <= 77
SELECT SUM(catalog_level_number), MAX(previous_entry_id) FROM Catalog_Contents

SELECT AVG(price_in_pounds), price_in_dollars FROM Catalog_Contents_Additional_Attributes JOIN Catalog_Contents JOIN Catalog_Structure ON Catalog_Structure.catalog_level_number = Catalog_Contents_Additional_Attributes.catalog_level_number AND Catalog_Contents.catalog_level_number = Catalog_Structure.catalog_level_number AND Catalog_Contents_Additional_Attributes.catalog_entry_id = Catalog_Contents.catalog_entry_id WHERE  Catalog_Contents_Additional_Attributes.catalog_level_number < 24 ORDER BY price_in_dollars DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT catalog_publisher), price_in_euros, attribute_value FROM Catalog_Contents_Additional_Attributes JOIN Catalogs JOIN Catalog_Contents JOIN Catalog_Structure ON Catalog_Structure.catalog_id = Catalogs.catalog_id AND Catalog_Structure.catalog_level_number = Catalog_Contents_Additional_Attributes.catalog_level_number AND Catalog_Contents.catalog_level_number = Catalog_Structure.catalog_level_number AND Catalog_Contents_Additional_Attributes.catalog_entry_id = Catalog_Contents.catalog_entry_id WHERE  next_entry_id >= 100 AND price_in_euros >= (SELECT SUM(price_in_euros) FROM Catalog_Contents WHERE  catalog_level_number != 86)
SELECT catalog_id, catalog_level_number FROM Catalog_Structure WHERE  catalog_level_number <= 0 GROUP BY catalog_id HAVING SUM(catalog_level_number) <= 23
SELECT AVG(catalog_id) FROM Catalog_Structure WHERE catalog_level_number BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  catalog_id <= 98 LIMIT 2
SELECT catalog_id FROM Catalogs WHERE  catalog_id = 96 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Catalog_Structure AS a WHERE Catalogs.catalog_id = a.catalog_id)
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT date_of_latest_revision) FROM Catalogs JOIN Catalog_Structure ON Catalog_Structure.catalog_id = Catalogs.catalog_id WHERE  catalog_level_number < 87
SELECT s.catalog_id, s.catalog_publisher FROM Catalogs AS s WHERE s.catalog_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 ORDER BY s.catalog_id DESC
SELECT catalog_entry_id, attribute_value FROM Catalog_Contents_Additional_Attributes WHERE  catalog_entry_id < 45 ORDER BY catalog_entry_id ASC LIMIT 3

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT date_of_publication), catalog_publisher FROM Catalogs WHERE catalog_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR date_of_publication NOT IN (SELECT date_of_publication FROM Catalogs AS h WHERE h.catalog_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  h.catalog_id < 73) GROUP BY catalog_publisher HAVING SUM(catalog_id) <= 59 ORDER BY catalog_publisher ASC

SELECT AVG(catalog_entry_id), COUNT(DISTINCT price_in_pounds), capacity FROM Catalogs JOIN Catalog_Contents JOIN Catalog_Structure ON Catalog_Structure.catalog_id = Catalogs.catalog_id AND Catalog_Contents.catalog_level_number = Catalog_Structure.catalog_level_number WHERE Catalog_Structure.catalog_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  parent_entry_id != 55 GROUP BY capacity HAVING MAX(catalog_entry_id) < 38 ORDER BY capacity ASC

SELECT MAX(f.catalog_id), f.catalog_id, f.catalog_publisher, Catalogs.catalog_publisher FROM Catalogs JOIN Catalogs AS f ON Catalogs.catalog_id = f.catalog_id WHERE Catalogs.catalog_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  f.catalog_id = 4 GROUP BY Catalogs.catalog_publisher HAVING AVG(f.catalog_id) <= 3 LIMIT 7
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT price_in_pounds), capacity FROM Catalog_Contents WHERE price_in_dollars BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  catalog_entry_id >= 72

SELECT MIN(previous_entry_id), COUNT(DISTINCT price_in_dollars) FROM Catalog_Contents_Additional_Attributes JOIN Catalog_Contents JOIN Catalog_Structure ON Catalog_Structure.catalog_level_number = Catalog_Contents_Additional_Attributes.catalog_level_number AND Catalog_Contents.catalog_level_number = Catalog_Structure.catalog_level_number AND Catalog_Contents_Additional_Attributes.catalog_entry_id = Catalog_Contents.catalog_entry_id WHERE  attribute_id < 66
SELECT v.catalog_level_name, v.catalog_level_name FROM Catalog_Structure AS v WHERE  v.catalog_level_number != 78 ORDER BY v.catalog_level_name DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT price_in_pounds), capacity FROM Catalogs JOIN Catalog_Contents JOIN Catalog_Structure ON Catalog_Structure.catalog_id = Catalogs.catalog_id AND Catalog_Contents.catalog_level_number = Catalog_Structure.catalog_level_number WHERE price_in_dollars BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND previous_entry_id >= (SELECT SUM(previous_entry_id) FROM Catalog_Contents AS w WHERE w.catalog_level_number BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  w.next_entry_id > 22 LIMIT 10) LIMIT 5
SELECT MIN(catalog_level_number), COUNT(DISTINCT catalog_level_number), catalog_level_name, catalog_id FROM Catalog_Structure WHERE  catalog_id != 31 GROUP BY catalog_id

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT catalog_name), COUNT(DISTINCT date_of_latest_revision), COUNT(DISTINCT catalog_level_name), Catalog_Structure.catalog_id FROM Catalogs JOIN Catalog_Structure ON Catalog_Structure.catalog_id = Catalogs.catalog_id WHERE  Catalogs.catalog_id = 1 GROUP BY Catalog_Structure.catalog_id ORDER BY Catalog_Structure.catalog_id DESC
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT next_entry_id), width FROM Catalog_Contents WHERE  next_entry_id != 94 ORDER BY width ASC LIMIT 5

SELECT price_in_pounds, product_stock_number FROM Catalog_Contents JOIN Catalog_Structure ON Catalog_Contents.catalog_level_number = Catalog_Structure.catalog_level_number WHERE catalog_entry_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Catalog_Contents_Additional_Attributes WHERE  attribute_id > 74 AND Catalog_Contents.catalog_entry_id = catalog_entry_id LIMIT 7) LIMIT 3
SELECT width FROM Catalog_Contents JOIN Catalog_Structure ON Catalog_Contents.catalog_level_number = Catalog_Structure.catalog_level_number

SELECT catalog_level_name, attribute_value FROM Catalog_Contents_Additional_Attributes JOIN Catalog_Structure ON Catalog_Structure.catalog_level_number = Catalog_Contents_Additional_Attributes.catalog_level_number WHERE  attribute_id > 10

SELECT previous_entry_id, height, date_of_latest_revision FROM Catalogs JOIN Catalog_Contents JOIN Catalog_Structure ON Catalog_Structure.catalog_id = Catalogs.catalog_id AND Catalog_Contents.catalog_level_number = Catalog_Structure.catalog_level_number WHERE  Catalog_Contents.catalog_level_number != 14 GROUP BY date_of_latest_revision ORDER BY previous_entry_id DESC LIMIT 7

SELECT MAX(Catalog_Structure.catalog_level_number), Catalog_Structure.catalog_level_number FROM Catalog_Structure AS z JOIN Catalog_Structure ON Catalog_Structure.catalog_level_number = z.catalog_level_number WHERE  Catalog_Structure.catalog_id != 1 ORDER BY Catalog_Structure.catalog_level_number ASC
